OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally dry across the area
OL,6,Fwith bright spells, although rather
OL,7,Fcloudy at times. Some sunnier spells
OL,8,Fmay develop later in the afternoon.
OL,9,FWinds light across most of the region,
OL,10,Fbut perhaps breezier towards the
OL,11,FLincolnshire coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPlenty of clear spells going
OL,14,Finto the evening and turning chilly.
OL,15,FCloudier conditions soon developing
OL,16,Fnear the coast and perhaps spreading
OL,17,Ffurther inland later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
