OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA bright day with mainly fine,
OL,6,Fdry weather and light winds. Plenty of
OL,7,Fsunny spells initially, but sunshine
OL,8,Fperhaps becoming hazy during the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Risk of patchy rain
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,13,Fand bright for Tuesday and Thursday
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells, though cloudier on
OL,15,FWednesday with a few spots of rain.
OL,16,FBreezy at times and turning warmer,
OL,17,Fperhaps hot by Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
